text: Bikkulovo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Bikkulovsky Selsoviet, Miyakinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 200 as of 2010. There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 16 km from Kirgiz-Miyaki, 15 km from Sadovy. == References == Category:Rural localities in Miyakinsky District
title: Bikkulovo, Miyakinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
